<DATELINE>GDANSK, Poland (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Police converged on strikebound coal mines
and a port, activists said Thursday, after more workers joined
stoppages and Solidarity denounced official repression of the
protests.
   The government and workers are struggling for the initiative in
the biggest labor upheaval since Gen. Wojciech Jaruzelski imposed
