for a challenge to a Polaroid Corp. stock plan designed to impede a
hostile takeover of the instant photography pioneer.
   Carolyn Berger, vice chancellor of Delaware's Court of Chancery,
scheduled Oct. 19-25 for hearings on Shamrock's suit, a court clerk
