<HEAD>Honda Posts $194 Million In Quarterly Profit</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Honda Motor Co. Ltd. reported Wednesday its
consolidated net earnings in the three-month period ended last June
30 totaled 26.0 billion yen, or about $194 million at current
exchange rates.
   The company changed its fiscal period from one ending on the
