<HEAD>Cabinet Minister Fires State Oil Company's President</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BOGOTA, Colombia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The president of Colombia's state oil
company Ecopetrol was fired Wednesday because of disagreements with
